headline: Nvidia And These AI Plays Lead 5 Stocks Near Buy Points
summary: Nvidia, touted as the "de facto AI infrastructure company" in a Friday note, and Coherent, another AI data center play, lead this weekend's watch list of five stocks near buy points.  In addition to NVDA and COHR, construction-equipment supplier United Rentals has data center exposure.  Nvidia has a 99 IBD Composite Rating out of a possible 99, according to IBD Stock Checkup.

headline: United Rentals (URI): Analyst Upgrades Spark Fresh Valuation Debate as Growth Optimism Grows
summary: United Rentals (NYSE:URI) just saw a round of upgrades from analysts like Baird, who point to signs of stabilization across the rental industry and renewed optimism for the company’s ability to drive future growth. See our latest analysis for United Rentals. United Rentals’ stock is showing signs of renewed momentum as confidence grows around the industry’s stabilization and its specialty rental push.
